    "title": "Schoolnet India is Hiring: Subject Matter Expert (Lead)",
    "description": "Schoolnet India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Subject Matter Expert at our Ahmedabad location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Schoolnet India:\nSchoolnet India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Collaborate with faculty on curriculum development initiatives\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Participate in school events, workshops, and training programs\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Educational Technology\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n• Proficiency in Bloom's Taxonomy\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Flexible working hours\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Learning & development budget\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Schoolnet India!",
